NAME

  dtol - convert DOS formatted text files into Linux formatted text files

SYNOPSIS

  dtol (flags)

DESCRIPTION

  dtol is designed to convert a DOS formatted text file into a Linux formatted
  text file. dtol will convert each carriage return and line feed end of line
  characters sequence to a line feed character only.

FLAGS

  -i  input file
  -o  output file
  -v  display version
  -s  report statistics
  -w  write over mode (input file will be overwritten as output)

  Standard input and output are assumed if no file names were specified.

